      "span_text": "HDL and purified PON1 inhibit the modification of LDL by HAECs.  HAECs pretreated with concentrated (Ϸ10-fold) supernatants containing PON3 protein are less effective in modifying LDL (as measured by the induction of monocyte chemotactic activity) than are HAECs pretreated with concentrated supernatants from uninduced HeLa-Tet-PON3 cells ( Figure 4A )."
